Setup on RStudio Cloud

  1. Sign up for RStudio Cloud or log in using your preferred credentials.

Setup on RStudio Cloud

  1. Once logged in, select the “New Project” dropdown in “Your Workspace” and select “New project from Git Repository”.

Setup on RStudio Cloud

  1. Enter the link to the class GitHub repository (https://github.com/SISBID/Data-Wrangling) and click “OK”. The project will take a bit of time to deploy.

Setup on RStudio Cloud

  1. You should now see files listed in your workspace (including some datasets well be using). Feel free to change any files here - they are yours now! For the most up-to-date versions of files, please visit the website: http://sisbid.github.io/Data-Wrangling/.
